  "title": "Logistics Operations Executive (3PL Logistics MNC)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a Global MNC, one of the leading players in the 3PL Logistics sector. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Logistics Operations Executive to be part of their Operations team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the east - easily accessible.</strong></p><p>The Logistics Operations Executive's responsible is:</p><ul><li>Oversee daily warehouse activities, including inbound, storage, picking, and outbound operations.</li><li>Coordinate with clients on orders, inventory management, and service requirements.</li><li>Track key KPIs such as delivery performance, inventory accuracy, and fulfillment rates.</li><li>Ensure adherence to company policies, safety standards, and regulatory guidelines.</li><li>Support WMS/TMS implementation, updates, and basic troubleshooting.</li><li>Work with transport partners to ensure timely dispatch and delivery.</li><li>Analyze operational data and prepare reports with improvement recommendations.</li><li>Drive continuous improvement initiatives to enhance efficiency and cost control.</li><li>Supervise and support junior or contract staff when needed.</li></ul><p>Job Requirements:</p><ul><li>Min 2 years of 3PL warehouse operations experience</li><li>Familiar with WMS and inventory management</li><li>Experience in leading a team</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.<br />We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p>Email Address: <strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p><p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.<br />EA License No. 19C9682<br />EA Reg. No. R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</p>",
